This project is a website aimed for user who don't want to sped too much money at lunch time.

Midipascher.fr allows you to find restaurants whose menus fit in your "ticket restaurant".

Midipascher.fr allows you to answer that familiar question : 'what will we have for lunch today?' at lower cost.

The website is written in java, aimed to run on a servlet container.

It allows a restaurant owner to register its restaurant, update restaurant information, unregister restaurant
It allow an admin to create/update/delete restaurant
It allows an admin to create/update/delete reference data
It allows a customer to find a restaurant based on geo informations.
It allows a customer to save searches.

Have fun on midipascher.fr
